You can! :-)

Contrary to what Bentley says, I would disconnect the vacuum line and run it directly from the distributor to the carb. With it connected, vacuum advance is disabled in gears 1-3 and I see no need to do that when you are trading engine life for a limited improvement in exhaust emissions.

